Class OFFlowTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openflow.protocol.table.OFFlowTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class OFFlowTable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    OFFlowTable describes the openflow table information

    OFFlowTable
    {
    int8 command;
    int8 tableId;
    int8 tableType;
    int8 matchFieldNum;
    int32 tableSize;

    int16 keyLength;
    int8 reserve[6];

    int8 tableName[OFGlobal.OFP_NAME_MAX_LENGTH];

    List<OFMatch20> matchFieldList;
    } //sizeof() = 16 + OFGlobal.OFP_NAME_MAX_LENGTH

    Author:
    Song Jian (jack.songjian@huawei.com), Huawei Technologies Co., Ltd.
